---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const PageTitle = 'Portfolio';
const Description = "Welcome to my Portfolio"; 
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle = {PageTitle} siteDescription={Description}>
    
    <!--the wrapper needs to control the size-->
    <div class="hero-projects-container">

        <img class="hero-projects" src="../../src/images/code.png" alt="Code Editor Image" />
        <h1>Projects</h1>
    </div>
    <p>Below you will find Projects that i have worked on that I think are some of my best work. In each Project you will find a link to the project or images of the Project If the application is no longer in opperation. I will include links to the code for each project if it is publicly available.</p>
    <hr/>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .hero-projects-container{
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
    }
    .hero-projects{
        width: 80%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: block;
    }

    h1{
        background: #fff;
        color:var(--DarkBlue);
        width: 50%;
        bottom: -20px;
        right: 30%;
        position: absolute;
        font-size: 300%;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-align: right;

    }

    @media (min-width: 1000px){
        .hero-projects{
            width:700px;
        }
    }
</style>

